{"tid":1375782,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【世界一姐】江旻憓十字韌帶撕裂 東京奧運港重劍隊爭牌遇挫折","createTime":"2019-07-28T06:50:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T07:15:04.000Z","uid":20916,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"90f48e07ef055e86b5f64d0d562fb956e9f0ea7c","tid":1375782,"uid":20916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T06:50:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190728/large/1564295180_1258.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190728%2Flarge%2F1564295180_1258.jpg&h=78477f03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n女子重劍世界一姐江旻憓（Vivian）上周勇奪世錦賽個人賽銅牌，可惜她比賽時觸傷右膝，賽後即返港治理，Vivian昨於個人Instagram報訊，透露她右膝十字韌帶撕裂，已動手術根治。前年江旻憓左膝十字韌帶亦曾斷裂，當時她養傷數月即復出，現時距東京奧運開幕約一年，如Vivian康復程度如前年般理想，相信她能及時痊癒重拾狀態。<br />\n<br />\nVivian早前於匈牙利世錦賽奪銅創港將歷來最佳，本來她會續留當地再戰團體賽，然而她戰罷個人賽旋即回港，當時她憶述出戰八強前不慎滑倒，觸傷右膝，被逼返港治理，「八強時我一發力，右腳後筋會『撻一聲』，腳軟無力，鬆咗咁。」她指醫生即場檢查表示沒有大礙，可繼續比賽，惟她比賽翌晨起床即發現膝關節不能彎曲，傷勢嚴重。事隔一周，Vivian再於個人instagram上載她躺在病床上的照片，表示自己右膝十字韌帶撕裂，並已動手術治理，感謝各界關心。<br />\n<br />\n記者：洪量丰<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20190728/59871896\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190728%2F59871896&d=GsYKB4iL2zhb3369BxXbpw9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=0099f0dc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190728%2F59871896&h=407fdd7d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20190728/59871896</a>"},{"pid":"90c26dbc68b55146c8f73edaa5154e73c05cde30","tid":1375782,"uid":166474,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T06:52:37.000Z","msg":"omg，基本上女重得佢一個carry，佢傷左連團體都打埋柴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b600e55ae9a93778448e9acbd0ddeeeb0346f658","tid":1375782,"uid":46551,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T07:15:04.000Z","msg":"acl 咁大獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}